From William VanHorne Subject Re Why did they behave as they did Waco reading suggestion In article Phil Fraering writes How come noone mentions Eric Hoffer when talking about fanatic behavior anymore Good If you haven't read The True Believer by Eric Hoffer do so at your first I don't know why Hoffer is out of style now but The True Believer is still the best explanation of nutball behavior ever Bill VanHorne